   "source": [
    "# 8.3 知识蒸馏 (Knowledge Distillation)\n",
    "\n",
    "知识蒸馏将大模型（教师）的知识迁移到小模型（学生），使小模型在保持效率的同时获得接近大模型的性能。\n",
    "\n",
    "本节涵盖：\n",
    "- 经典蒸馏\n",
    "- 中间层蒸馏\n",
    "- LLM蒸馏"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 经典蒸馏\n",
    "\n",
    "**目的**：用教师模型的软标签训练学生模型\n",
    "\n",
    "**基本原理**：教师模型输出的概率分布（软标签）包含比硬标签更丰富的信息（类间关系），学生模型通过模仿教师的输出分布来学习这些暗知识。\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心公式**：\n",
    "- L = α × L_hard + (1-α) × L_soft\n",
    "- L_soft = KL(σ(z_s/T) || σ(z_t/T)) × T²\n",
    "- T是温度参数，T越大分布越平滑，暴露更多类间关系"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class TeacherModel(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.net = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(64, 256), nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(256, 128), nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(128, 10))\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return self.net(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "class StudentModel(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.net = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(64, 64), nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(64, 10))\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return self.net(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "teacher = TeacherModel()\n",
    "student = StudentModel()\n",
    "\n",
    "x = torch.randn(16, 64)\n",
    "labels = torch.randint(0, 10, (16,))\n",
    "\n",
    "with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "    teacher_logits = teacher(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "student_logits = student(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "T = 4.0\n",
    "soft_teacher = F.log_softmax(teacher_logits / T, dim=-1)\n",
    "soft_student = F.log_softmax(student_logits / T, dim=-1)\n",
    "soft_target = F.softmax(teacher_logits / T, dim=-1)\n",
    "\n",
    "loss_soft = F.kl_div(soft_student, soft_target, reduction='batchmean') * (T * T)\n",
    "loss_hard = F.cross_entropy(student_logits, labels)\n",
    "alpha = 0.7\n",
    "total_loss = alpha * loss_hard + (1 - alpha) * loss_soft\n",
    "\n",
    "teacher_params = sum(p.numel() for p in teacher.parameters())\n",
    "student_params = sum(p.numel() for p in student.parameters())\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Classic Knowledge Distillation ===')\n",
    f"print(f'Teacher: {teacher_params:,} params, Student: {student_params:,} params ({student_params/teacher_params:.1%})')\n",
    "print(f'\\nTemperature T={T}:')\n",
    "print(f'  Hard loss (CE): {loss_hard.item():.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'  Soft loss (KL): {loss_soft.item():.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'  Total loss: {total_loss.item():.4f}')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\nSoft label comparison (sample 0):')\n",
    "print(f'  Teacher (T=1): {F.softmax(teacher_logits[0], dim=-1).topk(3)}')\n",
    "print(f'  Teacher (T={T:.0f}): {F.softmax(teacher_logits[0]/T, dim=-1).topk(3)}')\n",
    "print(f'  Higher T -> smoother distribution -> more \"dark knowledge\"')\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: Soft labels contain inter-class relationships that hard labels miss.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 中间层蒸馏与LLM蒸馏\n",
    "\n",
    "**中间层蒸馏**：不仅蒸馏最终输出，还让学生模型的中间层表征匹配教师模型的中间层，提供更丰富的监督信号。\n",
    "\n",
    "**LLM蒸馏**：将大语言模型的能力蒸馏到小模型，常用方法：\n",
    "- **黑盒蒸馏**：只用大模型的输出作为训练数据，不需要访问内部\n",
    "- **白盒蒸馏**：访问大模型的logits和中间层\n",
    "- **合成数据蒸馏**：用大模型生成高质量训练数据\n",
    "\n",
    "**代表**：Alpaca（GPT-4→LLaMA）、Vicuna、Orca"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class TeacherWithHidden(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.layer1 = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(64, 128), nn.ReLU())\n",
    "        self.layer2 = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(128, 128), nn.ReLU())\n",
    "        self.layer3 = nn.Linear(128, 10)\n",
    "    def forward(self, x, return_hidden=False):\n",
    "        h1 = self.layer1(x)\n",
    "        h2 = self.layer2(h1)\n",
    "        out = self.layer3(h2)\n",
    "        if return_hidden:\n",
    "            return out, [h1, h2]\n",
    "        return out\n",
    "\n",
    "class StudentWithHidden(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.layer1 = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(64, 32), nn.ReLU())\n",
    "        self.layer2 = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(32, 32), nn.ReLU())\n",
    "        self.layer3 = nn.Linear(32, 10)\n",
    "        self.proj1 = nn.Linear(32, 128)\n",
    "        self.proj2 = nn.Linear(32, 128)\n",
    "    def forward(self, x, return_hidden=False):\n",
    "        h1 = self.layer1(x)\n",
    "        h2 = self.layer2(h1)\n",
    "        out = self.layer3(h2)\n",
    "        if return_hidden:\n",
    "            return out, [self.proj1(h1), self.proj2(h2)]\n",
    "        return out\n",
    "\n",
    "teacher = TeacherWithHidden()\n",
    "student = StudentWithHidden()\n",
    "x = torch.randn(16, 64)\n",
    "\n",
    "with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "    t_out, t_hidden = teacher(x, return_hidden=True)\n",
    "s_out, s_hidden = student(x, return_hidden=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "logit_loss = F.kl_div(F.log_softmax(s_out / 4.0, dim=-1), F.softmax(t_out / 4.0, dim=-1), reduction='batchmean') * 16\n",
    "hidden_losses = [F.mse_loss(sh, th) for sh, th in zip(s_hidden, t_hidden)]\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Intermediate Layer Distillation ===')\n",
    "print(f'Logit distillation loss: {logit_loss.item():.4f}')\n",
    "for i, hl in enumerate(hidden_losses):\n",
    "    print(f'Hidden layer {i} distillation loss: {hl.item():.4f}')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\n=== LLM Distillation Approaches ===')\n",
    "print(f'Black-box: Use teacher outputs as training data (easiest)')\n",
    "print(f'White-box: Access teacher logits + hidden states (best quality)')\n",
    "print(f'Synthetic: Generate data with teacher, train student from scratch')\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: More supervision signals (hidden states) -> better student performance.')"
   ]
  }
